- Install python3
- Install pip
- pip install -r requirements.txt
- Add a bot at https://discordapp.com/developers/applications/me
- Add a bot user for the bot
- Add the bot to your server with https://discordapp.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=<your client id here>&scope=bot
- Click to reveal the token
- Copy config.json.example to config.json and alter the value for "token"
- Optionally alter the value for "image_dir" and "database" if you want downloaded images/sqlite database stored somewhere else.
